This paper discusses the challenges and solutions for achieving ultra-low latency in 5G millimeter wave cellular networks, which involves topics related to network infrastructure, communication protocols, and information theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.AR (Hardware Architecture), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
